data.description: Cozy 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home with plenty of space, just a stone's throw away from downtown. This welcoming residence features a spacious layout, making it ideal for a growing family or those who value room to spread out. The kitchen is equipped for easy meal prep, and the outdoor area provides a perfect spot for relaxation. With convenient parking and a prime location near downtown St. Joe, this home offers a comfortable and practical urban living experience. Schedule a viewing today and discover the charm of this conveniently located property!
